Package: almanac
Title: Tools for Adjusting and Generating Dates Using a Grammar
    of Schedules
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Davis",
           family = "Vaughan",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "davis@rstudio.com")
Description: Provides tools for defining events and schedules.
    These provide a system for generating dates in a schedule, adjusting
    them relative to a schedule, and determining if they are included in a
    schedule.
License: GPL-3 + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/DavisVaughan/almanac
BugReports: https://github.com/DavisVaughan/almanac/issues
